[LEONARD] Wow.

9
00:00:21,229 --> 00:00:22,522
You’re mad at me, right?

10
00:00:22,939 --> 00:00:24,816
Take your anger out on me.

11
00:00:25,275 --> 00:00:26,735
You finally showed up!

12
00:00:26,943 --> 00:00:28,153
I’m impressed, Liv!

13
00:00:28,695 --> 00:00:29,362
Hi, ma’am.

14
00:00:29,363 --> 00:00:30,446
