15
00:00:30,447 --> 00:00:32,115
but this is a restricted area.

16
00:00:32,615 --> 00:00:34,241
I’ll just visit the patient.

17
00:00:34,242 --> 00:00:37,203
Kirby. It’s fine. Let her in.

18
00:00:38,038 --> 00:00:39,164
How are you, Juro?

19
00:00:39,414 --> 00:00:40,707
I’m fine, Aunt.

20
00:00:41,374 --> 00:00:42,333
She is your godmother?

21
00:00:42,584 --> 00:00:44,084
I’m Irene Zamora.

22
00:00:44,085 --> 00:00:44,836
The surname of-

23
00:00:44,836 --> 00:00:45,628
Yes.

24
00:00:45,629 --> 00:00:46,629
Zach’s mom.

25
00:00:47,255 --> 00:00:48,506
Uncle Leonard’s wife.

26
00:00:48,965 --> 00:00:50,592
You’re disgusting.

27
00:00:51,176 --> 00:00:52,926
How could you abuse your own son?

28
00:00:52,927 --> 00:00:53,928
Your own blood.

29
00:00:54,888 --> 00:00:55,805
My God.

30
00:00:56,473 --> 00:00:58,808
You let your own son be used
by multiple people?

31
00:00:59,350 --> 00:01:01,060
To be abused over and over?

32
00:01:01,061 --> 00:01:02,729
What kind of a father are you?

33
00:01:02,896 --> 00:01:04,105
You said it yourself.

34
00:01:04,689 --> 00:01:05,814
He’s my blood.

35
00:01:05,815 --> 00:01:08,109
I can do whatever I want to.

36
00:01:08,610 --> 00:01:09,319
Liv!

37
00:01:10,195 --> 00:01:10,904
[LEONARD GROANS]

38
00:01:11,863 --> 00:01:12,489
[LIV AND LEONARD GRUNTS]

39
00:01:12,489 --> 00:01:13,114
Come here.
Come here!

40
00:01:13,114 --> 00:01:13,907
[LIV SCREAMS]

41
00:01:16,076 --> 00:01:16,785
[LIV GRUNTS]

42
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:18,411
Sugar!

43
00:01:18,453 --> 00:01:19,370
[SUGAR SCREAMS]

44
00:01:19,913 --> 00:01:20,747
Yana!

45
00:01:20,747 --> 00:01:21,206
Yana!

46
00:01:21,206 --> 00:01:21,956
Dad!
[GUNSHOT]

47
00:01:23,374 --> 00:01:23,792
[LIV] Uncle!

48
00:01:23,792 --> 00:01:24,209
Dad!

49
00:01:24,209 --> 00:01:24,876
[LIV] Yana!

50
